Name: PUSH
About the game: New puzzler from the creators of 'Klocki', 'Zenge', 'Hook' and 'Art of Gravity'. Like our previous games, its intended to be a relaxing experience, thus there are no points, stars, tutorials, move counters. Your goal is to push all the buttons. How do you do it? Well, thats the puzzle...
